<concept xml:lang="en-us" id="relax-ng-constraint-module-coding-requirements" >
 <title>RELAX NG: Coding requirements for
    <?oxy_delete author="chris" timestamp="20200705T161303-0400" content="constraint"?><?oxy_insert_start author="chris" timestamp="20200705T161303-0400"?>content
    model specialization<?oxy_insert_end?> modules</title>
 <shortdesc>A
    <?oxy_delete author="chris" timestamp="20200705T161320-0400" content="structural constraint"?><?oxy_insert_start author="chris" timestamp="20200705T161322-0400"?>content
    model specialization<?oxy_insert_end?> module defines the
    <?oxy_delete author="chris" timestamp="20200705T161336-0400" content="constraints"?><?oxy_insert_start author="chris" timestamp="20200705T161336-0400"?>modified
    content model or attribute list<?oxy_insert_end?> for a map or topic element type. A domain
    constraint module defines the constraints for an element or attribute domain.</shortdesc>
